<!--
    Ukrainian (uk) — Cyrillic script.
    The existing Russian locale (values-ru/) already exercises the Cyrillic
    font stack, so no additional font or rendering work is required.
    Key differences from Russian to watch out for:
      • Ukrainian uses "і" (U+0456) and "ї" (U+0457), not found in Russian.
      • Genitive plural of "день" (day) is "днів" in Ukrainian vs "дней" in Russian.
      • "Налаштування" (settings) vs Russian "Настройки".
      • "Зберегти" (save) vs Russian "Сохранить".
-->
